{"tid":1021875,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【小背心】李彩華情人節宣布結婚嫁內地富商：Rain + Eric = Mr & Mrs Huang","createTime":"2019-02-14T14:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T16:13:24.000Z","uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2f56fab4e060602b2654e8b3515ced64d14ad46f","tid":1021875,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2270000/2271612/wedding_thumb_20190214_J_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2270000%2F2271612%2Fwedding_thumb_20190214_J_1024.jpg&h=aca089db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李彩華情人節宣布結婚嫁內地富商：Rain + Eric = Mr &amp; Mrs Huang<br />\n 娛樂 16:25 2019/02/14 <br />\n<br />\n現年35歲的李彩華（前藝名：李彩樺）於2月14日情人節宣布閃婚喜訊！李彩華在微博上載Q版公仔的情侶照片，透露老公就是拍拖半年、早前被傳媒影到在街頭甜蜜餵食的男友Eric！<br />\n<br />\n近年主力內地發展的李彩華，於去年初承認與「新五虎」何遠恆結束3年情，但她已極速走出情傷回復勇態，不時在微博上載靚相。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2270000/2271612/12_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2270000%2F2271612%2F12_1024.jpeg&h=82fc442d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日有媒體影到難得回港的李彩華拍拖近照，見她與六呎高的猛男牽手街頭、互相餵食。報道一出，李彩華便於今日2月14日情人節下午在微博公布閃婚喜訊，她分享了一張2人的Q版公仔的合照以及紅封包照片，並謂：<br />\n<br />\n#甜蜜情人節##寶寶的少女心# <br />\nRain + Eric = Mr &amp; Mrs Huang<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2270000/2271612/14_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2270000%2F2271612%2F14_1024.jpeg&h=7a3e0f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文中透露老公正是日前被影到的​​​​身高6呎、38歲的男友Eric，李彩華表示丈夫姓黃，於內地經營鋼鐵生意，選擇情人節公布喜訊非刻意安排，只是巧合。<br />\n<br />\n有指男方在去年得知李彩華單身後，不時到劇組探班力追對方，終於得到女神芳心，拍拖半年已經極速閃婚！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2270000/2271612/5ac1609egy1fzgf5adblgj21hn1zk4qt_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2270000%2F2271612%2F5ac1609egy1fzgf5adblgj21hn1zk4qt_1024.jpg&h=c059db97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n17歲入行的「小背心」李彩華，出道有「小陳慧琳」稱號，後被指原來要為父母還百萬欠債，努力多年終還清債項，孝感動天。全力赴內地掘金的她憑劇集《回家的誘惑》走紅，劇接劇工作不斷，據稱3年間吸金過億。<br />\n<br />\n間中回港的她，常被拍到去名店血拼，她亦提過母親是其理財顧問，最愛買磚頭保值，至少持有4個物業，身家估計8,000萬元，有樓有cash！<br />\n<br />\n撰文 : TOPick柴犬出動<br />\n<br />\n轉自香港經濟日報網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2271612/李彩華情人節宣布結婚嫁內地富商：Rain%20-%20Eric%20-%20Mr%20-%20Mrs%20Huang\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2271612%2F%E6%9D%8E%E5%BD%A9%E8%8F%AF%E6%83%85%E4%BA%BA%E7%AF%80%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A%E5%AB%81%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AF%8C%E5%95%86%EF%BC%9ARain%2520-%2520Eric%2520-%2520Mr%2520-%2520Mrs%2520Huang&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDnG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=9deb656d\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2271612/李彩華情人節宣布結婚嫁內地富商：Rain%20-%20Eric%20-%20Mr%20-%20Mrs%20Huang</a>"},{"pid":"f2134d5d1b56889bbc4951bd211de3c298090ecb","tid":1021875,"uid":35221,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161125/large/25ec3p9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161125%2Flarge%2F25ec3p9e.jpg&h=27e21865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知香港海鮮業聯合總會主席李彩華會唔會都去飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2261976f8a16586f7fa99845b59c0008224672ac","tid":1021875,"uid":78429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:28:05.000Z","msg":"是但啦"},{"pid":"48c9ad6e04628107cf089381b3c15aaf5da610dc","tid":1021875,"uid":55458,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:44:33.000Z","msg":"蛇精男害人不淺"},{"pid":"827747e3f1dee8ad2df4e58c9bb95f9ca86a67df","tid":1021875,"uid":79442,"like":3,"d